  "industry_note": "Inconel 738 / IN-738LC (Cannon-Muskegon) — vacuum-cast Ni-base γ' precipitation-hardened superalloy (Ni bal, Cr 16, Co 8.5, Mo 1.75, W 2.6, Ta 1.75, Nb 0.9, Al 3.4, Ti 3.4, B/Zr trace, C 0.11 (LC=0.10 low-C)). γ' ≈ 43 vol%. Investment Tmax 980°C continuous (oxidation 우수 — Cr 16% high). 산업 가스 터빈 first-stage blade (Siemens SGT-700/750, GE 7HA.02, Westinghouse W501F). 1965년 GE 개발."
